<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-73-0714 </DOCNO><TEXT>The report describes some techniques for the reduction of flicker causedby arc furnaces and the containment of voltage harmonics caused by disturbingloads. Also discussed is the attempt to establish an international normativeto regulate the connection of such loads to supply lines. In particular,the report considers the use of VAR control systems, thyristors and arcfurnaces fed by direct currents. Filters are prescribed for disturbingloads.</TEXT></DOC>